# Serializability

	A mechanism of writing the state of an object into byte-stream

# Deserializability

	converting byte-stream into an object

~ It is platform independent


# Serializable Interface

~ It is a marker interface, to add certain capability 

~ object with serializable implement can be used for Stream

# Methods

	ObjectOutputStream(OutputStream out): It creates an ObjectOutputStream that writes to the specified OutputStream.

	writeObject(Object obj): It writes the specified object to the ObjectOutputStream.

	flush(): It flushes the current output stream.

	close(): It closes the current output stream.

	ObjectInputStream(InputStream in): It creates an ObjectInputStream that reads from the specified InputStream.
	
	readObject(): It reads an object from the input stream.
	
	close(): It closes ObjectInputStream.



